---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<section class="hero">
  <h1>Take back control from gambling. For&nbsp;good.</h1>
  <p class="subtitle">
    BetBlocker is a free, open-source platform that blocks gambling across every
    device you own — with layers of protection designed to hold firm when
    willpower alone cannot.
  </p>
  <div class="cta-group">
    <a href={`${base}getting-started/`} class="btn-primary">
      Get Started Free
    </a>
    <a href="https://github.com/JerrettDavis/BetBlocker" class="btn-secondary">
      View on GitHub
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
